Note: Edge Case and Error Handling Tests

Process called "test_large_expansion_stack":
    Let context be MacroSystem.create_macro_context with config as None
    
    Note: Simulate deep expansion stack without hitting limit
    For i from 1 to 50:
        Let frame be MacroSystem.ExpansionFrame with:
            macro_name as "macro_" plus i
            input_tokens as list containing
            output_tokens as list containing
            variables as dictionary containing
            scope as "scope_" plus i
            depth as i
            metadata as dictionary containing
        Add frame to context.expansion_stack
    
    assert_equal(50, length of context.expansion_stack, "expansion_stack_size")

Note: Master Test Runner

Process called "run_all_system_tests":
    Display message "Advanced Macros System Module - Comprehensive Test Suite"
    Display message "=" repeated 60
    
    Note: Core System Tests
    Display message "\nCore System Tests:"
    test_create_macro_context_default_config()
    test_create_macro_context_custom_config()
    test_create_macro_registry()
    test_create_macro_cache()
    
    Note: Macro Registration Tests
    Display message "\nMacro Registration Tests:"
    test_register_macro_success()
    test_register_multiple_macros()
    test_register_macro_with_versioning()
    test_unregister_macro()
    test_unregister_nonexistent_macro()
    
    Note: Macro Expansion Tests
    Display message "\nMacro Expansion Tests:"
    test_expand_macro_basic()
    test_expand_nonexistent_macro()
    test_expand_macro_with_disabled_system()
    test_expansion_limit()
    
    Note: Macro Validation Tests
    Display message "\nMacro Validation Tests:"
    test_validate_macro_definition_valid()
    test_validate_macro_definition_empty_name()
    test_validate_macro_pattern()
    test_validate_macro_template()
    
    Note: Macro Compilation Tests
    Display message "\nMacro Compilation Tests:"
    test_compile_macro_definition()
    test_compile_macro_template()
    
    Note: Performance and Caching Tests
    Display message "\nPerformance and Caching Tests:"
    test_expansion_cache_functionality()
    test_performance_metrics_collection()
    
    Note: Utility Function Tests
    Display message "\nUtility Function Tests:"
    test_generate_expansion_cache_key()
    test_generate_scope_id()
    test_create_variable_mappings()
    
    Note: Edge Case Tests
    Display message "\nEdge Case Tests:"
    test_large_expansion_stack()
    
    Note: Display final results
    Display message "\n" plus "=" repeated 60
    Display message "System Module Test Results:"
    Display message "Total Tests: " plus test_count
    Display message "Tests Passed: " plus passed_count
    Display message "Tests Failed: " plus failed_count
    
    If failed_count is equal to 0:
        Display message "✅ ALL SYSTEM TESTS PASSED!"
    Otherwise:
        Display message "❌ " plus failed_count plus " TESTS FAILED"
    
    Display message "=" repeated 60

Note: Execute the test suite
run_all_system_tests()